<dl id="n06155m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06155m">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06155m"> 155(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> visit the sin upon</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">SECOND COMMANDMENT. &ldquo;THOU SHALT NOT MAKE TO THYSELF ANY GRAVEN IMAGE, NOR THE LIKENESS OF ANY THING THAT IS IN HEAVEN ABOVE, OR IN THE EARTH BENEATH, OR IN THE WATER UNDER THE EARTH. THOU SHALT NOT BOW DOWN TO THEM, NOR WORSHIP THEM; FOR I THE LORD THY GOD AM A JEALOUS GOD, AND <mark>VISIT THE SINS OF THE FATHERS UPON</mark> THE CHILDREN, UNTO THE THIRD AND FOURTH GENERATIONS OF THEM THAT HATE ME, AND SHOW MERCY UNTO THOUSANDS IN THEM THAT LOVE ME, AND KEEP MY COMMANDMENTS.&rdquo; <small> Anonymous, <a name="ATCC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ATCC"><cite title="source">Analysis of the Church Catechism</cite></a> (1879) 33-4</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
